cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.IT, cs.LG, cs.NE 

The paper deals with image compression using deep learning techniques, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and multimedia (cs.MM) sub-categories. It also involves distributed source coding (cs.IT) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.NE) techniques. Therefore, these five sub-categories are the most likely ones for this paper.
